%C A094951 Performing the same operation but using the multiplier [1 0 0] yields [3^n 2*A027471(n+1) A077616(n)]. Example: M^4 * [1 0 0] = [81 216 324] where 324 = A077616(4) and 216/2 = 108 = A027471(5).
